    <stitle>ELECTRICAL SYSTEM TROUBLESHOOTING GUIDE - 9800 - CAB - TILT: 9800 - OPERATION</stitle>
    <svcsection/>
    <svcsubsec>
        <title>OPERATION</title>
        <svcproc svcproctype="operate" graphiccount="0">
            <title>WINDSHIELD WIPERS</title>
            <para>The electric wiper/washer switches are located on the instrument wing panel to the right of the
                driver.
            </para>
            <para>Use the wiper speed control rocker switch to start and stop the wiper-only function and to control
                wiper speed, HIGH or LOW.
            </para>
            <para>Use the intermittent operation/washer control sliding (rheostat) switch to control intermittent wiper
                operation, and to operate the windshield washer.
            </para>
        </svcproc>
    </svcsubsec>
